file.name: swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Captcha API
  description: API Используемое для решения капчи на сайте fssp.gov.ru
  version: 0.0.1

servers:
  - url: http://0.0.0.0:1769
    description: Test server

paths:
  /solve: 
    get: 
      operationId: app.solve 
      parameters: 
        - name: image 
          description: Captcha to solve 
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
            format: base64
          required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Captcha text
          content: 
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  captcha_text:
                    type: string
                    example: пфк53
